{"id":"9e15d6b9-db29-498e-9d31-8754a115477e","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"Il a huit ans, les mains sales et les yeux trop grands.*\n\n\"Un petit sort ?","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T04:52:04.364392Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"0cf602c7-bac0-4f26-b4c4-6d108454f938","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"La magie c'est comme la musique : il ne faut pas chercher le plus fort, mais le plus juste.\"\n\n*Je sors une petite bille de verre incolore et la pose sur l'herbe.*\n\n\"{char.name} regarde pas la bille.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T04:52:04.379083Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"ba435e00-dbb3-46ad-80c7-39c39c53428e","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"Pense à quelque chose de chaud, comme un café brûlant que ta mère t'a donné sans faire attention.\"\n\n*Je murmure et la bille se met à flotter, entourée d'une flamme bleue.*\n\n\"C'était pas la bille.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T04:52:04.394686Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"e2667fdb-93ca-4ff5-938a-15c07f0e1511","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"Maintenant c'est toi qui fais la magie.\"","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T04:52:04.411509Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"e14d982b-a9db-4a92-8bad-808b53184185","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"*Je pose mon sac par terre, la poussière de la route sur mes bottes.*\n\n\"Je ne suis pas venu pour survivre.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T04:52:04.425073Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"b1c6fc69-ec83-4630-99ed-3499b32d45a8","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"Je suis venu parce que j'ai vu, il y a deux semaines, ce qui se passe dans les tranchées de l'est.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T04:52:04.439364Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"0e13a486-0e62-4877-8730-ae7b3c5fc737","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"Les assiégeants ne tiendront pas quinze jours.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T04:52:04.454825Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"da1005a5-26a3-48b5-afdd-096889e40a32","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"J'ai fait couler leurs bateaux sur la rivière.\"\n\n*Je lui pose les mains sur les épaules.*\n\n\"Mais il faut tromper l'ennemi.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T04:52:04.469891Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"0ee377ff-9f53-4c60-b048-892d995ae1f7","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"Fais du bruit, des feux de forge la nuit.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T04:52:04.485254Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"e4143697-d196-484d-8889-12420629fbcf","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"S'ils pensent qu'on a des nouvelles armes, ils hésiteront.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T04:52:04.499800Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"d3b5b274-34c7-49e7-889a-dcf6a5d1c606","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"Et l'hésitation, c'est déjà une victoire.\"\n\n*Je commence à défaire mon sac.*\n\n\"Et maintenant, montre-moi la carte du siège.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T04:52:04.515556Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
